snippet.title: Zoria Age of Shattering Prologue Launch Trailer
snippet.description: A turn-based, tactical, party-based RPG experience introducing the player to the world of Zoria. A unique story in a world filled with magic, ancient history and countless mysteries. Dangerous dungeons, epic fights, Close-quarters, ranged and melee combat, a story of discovery and adventure.
